snippet.title: Hollow Knight: Silksong - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
On September 4, ascend to the peak of a haunted kingdom in Hollow Knight: Silksong!

The game will be available for purchase on Steam, Nintendo Switch, Nintendo Switch 2, Xbox, Sony PlayStation 4, Sony PlayStation 5, and DRM free on GOG and Humble Bundle

Restorani jastog kavijar pa inda skampi

Cekaj me tu sam za minut 
Samo da svratim po pare tu kod kuce

Glava mi puknuce
Ovoliko stila 
Jaka rima
Mala cima
Svako bi da ovo ima

Jaka prica ista lica
Aj nas slikaj al bez blica
Kes kolica svaka zica 
Nama predena igrica
Ovo lito idemo espania ibiza
Italiano mafia spageti pizza

Quieres Pérignon?
Sí, señor!
Dodi idemo
Te amo mi amor
Mi casa es tu casa
Tamo se vidimo
Lito ti i ja terasa 
Ai se eu te pego
Gradom kruzimo
Para sada puni smo
Sunce vitar kabrio 
Scenu sam zapalio
Gori sve alo alo
Cao mala jel se znamo
Samo malo dodi vamo
Vodim te, reci kamo

Putting on a drum show.
 
Completed checklist for today,
Now they have to let you out of your cage,

Even now, even now,
He’ll take the longer way home,

Turns it up,

Two places he does not want to go, so, so.
 
I’ve been this way,
I want to change.

snippet.title: SEVERINA - ‘PUMPAJ, SEVE BRATE’
snippet.description:
☆ Subscribe Severina YouTube channel ► https://goo.gl/QNLWsB ↩︎
☆ Severina  - 'Pumpaj, Seve brate' 

➤ Instagram: https://instagram.com/severina
➤ Facebook: https://facebook.com/severina
➤ TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@severina.vuckovic
--------------------
➤Listen:

Deezer / Spotify / Apple Music / Amazon Music: https://bfan.link/pumpaj-seve-brate
--------------------

Severina  - 'Pumpaj, Seve brate'

Glazba i tekst: Severina Vučković
Aranžman: Zvonimir Horvat
Video: Fabrika Sarajevo
--------------------

TEKST:
(H)Eej kad bi bio malo muško,
da ispuniš želje i priznaš meni sve.
(H)Eej zašto nisi malo muško?
Priznao bi dragi, prizao bi sve.

Da si me lagao,
varao pa prodao,
a ja samo dinstala,
tebe čekala.
Zato pumpam svaki dan
da ti dignem pritisak.
Pumpam dragi ja, samo tenzija.

Na vjernost da se kunem
ti si mene tjerao.
Svilu, zlato obećao,
a maglu prodavao.
I kad lažes da si bolan,
rane sam ti vidala.
Ti da si muško, dragi,
ja bih suknju nosila.

Sjedila za mašinom i rupe ti krpila.
Dobra žena domaćica, večera te čekala.
Dok si muko belosvjetska na sve strane šarao,
djecu, brata, oca, majku, sve si razočarao.

#severina #pumpaj #volimstosevolimo #ljubavseljubavljuvraca #newsong

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunner Swap VS 2 Hunters
snippet.description:
This was crazy intense. Manhunt, but with a twist.

This video, I teamed up with my rival, Daquavis, in a new #MinecraftManhunt challenge. We have to speedrun and beat Minecraft against two hunters, but we swap who is playing every minute! It was hilarious and super intense.

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic


In this challenge Daquavis and I essentially are one player. We share an inventory, health, position, and basically everything else. The idea is that we are swapping who has control of one player. When we are swapped out, we don't know what is happening at all. We see a black screen and hear nothing.

This video was inspired by a similar challenge, without hunters, posted here: https://youtu.be/WU5etmP0h0Y?si=kzoxiP04YnD74_Ni

This was played on Minecraft 1.21.8, and is a custom coded challenge. There were a few bugs that we plan to iron out before we try something like this again!

300,000 likes for me to try this challenge with someone else!


George: @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap: @Sapnap 
Daquavis: @DaquavisMC 

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/DreamWasTaken

snippet.title: The Evolution of Furnace!
snippet.description:
From a forgotten Building to the center stage - the heroic tale of a fallen Card's second act

X ► https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashroyale
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashRoyale/

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale
